---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - AI Review Site" description="Learn more about our mission to provide comprehensive AI insights and reviews">
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 text-white py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">About AI Review Site</h1>
      <p class="text-xl opacity-90 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Your trusted source for comprehensive AI insights, detailed reviews, and cutting-edge analysis.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Content -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <h2>Our Mission</h2>
          <p>
            At AI Review Site, we're passionate about artificial intelligence and its transformative potential. 
            Our mission is to provide you with honest, comprehensive, and insightful reviews of AI tools, 
            technologies, and trends that are shaping our future.
          </p>

          <h2>What We Do</h2>
          <p>
            We specialize in:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>In-Depth Reviews:</strong> Comprehensive analysis of AI tools and platforms</li>
            <li><strong>Technology Insights:</strong> Deep dives into AI algorithms and methodologies</li>
            <li><strong>Industry Trends:</strong> Analysis of emerging AI trends and their implications</li>
            <li><strong>Practical Guides:</strong> How-to articles for implementing AI solutions</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Our Approach</h2>
          <p>
            We believe in providing unbiased, well-researched content that helps you make informed decisions 
            about AI technologies. Every review and analysis is based on thorough testing and research, 
            ensuring you get the most accurate and helpful information.
          </p>

          <h2>Stay Connected</h2>
          <p>
            Follow us for regular updates on the latest developments in artificial intelligence. 
            Whether you're a developer, business professional, or AI enthusiast, we have content 
            that will help you stay ahead of the curve.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg mt-8">
            <h3 class="text-blue-900">Ready to Explore?</h3>
            <p class="text-blue-800">
              Check out our latest articles and reviews to discover the most innovative AI solutions 
              and insights available today.
            </p>
            <a href="/blog" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors mt-4">
              Browse Our Articles
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose h2 {
    color: #111827;
    font-size: 1.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .prose h3 {
    color: #111827;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  
  .prose p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: #374151;
  }
  
  .prose ul {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .prose li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #374151;
  }
</style>
